  "body": "<p>One of the prompts at Two Peas this month is a focus on patterned papers. I decided to use my favorite combinations of patterns - woodgrain, polka dots and florals to create a colorful layout. I used some behind the scenes photos from the <a href=\"http://www.tbs.com/shows/trendswithbenefits/video/video-detail/hipster-scrapbooking\">TBS Trends With Benefits</a> shoot at Urbanic. Here is how <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1827078-trends-with-benefits-patterned-paper-only/\">this page</a> came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"11a-DSC_1723-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931413025-6POEDSSZCFA87Z4IJFR2/11a-DSC_1723-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"11b-DSC_1724-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931413285-640WU7C9UF4IZKYTEH4R/11b-DSC_1724-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11c-DSC_1725-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931415643-LTX0J6KZ430WFX7H6RUO/11c-DSC_1725-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11d-DSC_1726-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931415767-47T7GA311TYR0FAZPIMZ/11d-DSC_1726-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11ee-DSC_1728-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931417069-7S8H54Q4IDLS11J9G2BQ/11ee-DSC_1728-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11f-DSC_1731-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931417151-117FQMFTA473S0BSBI4W/11f-DSC_1731-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11g-DSC_1732-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931417543-60CIO4A56S10ULNZI74W/11g-DSC_1732-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11h-DSC_1733-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931417750-69R64II19BGZ9SMTAYM8/11h-DSC_1733-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11i-DSC_1734-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931417985-Q57UA2EJMKXGON30Y9J1/11i-DSC_1734-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11j-DSC_1735-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931418272-YNMZZEGNXIWYMLB7E06B/11j-DSC_1735-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11k-DSC_1738-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931418601-PPWPOG783INB0WHG1DNU/11k-DSC_1738-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11l-DSC_1747-598x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600931418949-GU4HWOR4SYBU1CUOZDC0/11l-DSC_1747-598x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If you're wondering, I did use the make up artist's hair as inspiration for the layout. <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1827078-trends-with-benefits-patterned-paper-only/\">Copyright Two Peas In A Bucket</a></p>"
